    Buy and sell rare vinyl records, LPs and CDs from Mynyl Vinyl.
    With so many vinyl record albums located in one place you will easily be able to find all the hard to find vinyl, 
    rare LP records and out-of-print 45 RPM singles that have been eluding you for years.
</p>